# Architecture Rules

## Component Pattern
Every component must follow this exact pattern:
const ComponentName = {
  render(data) { return `HTML string` },
  bind(element, callbacks) { /* only event listeners here */ }
}
export default ComponentName

## Layer Rules
- components/ → NO direct api.js calls, use callbacks only
- pages/ → orchestrates components + api calls
- core/ → NO UI logic, NO direct DOM manipulation
- utils/ → pure functions only, NO dependencies on other layers

## Config Rule
All hardcoded values (colors, texts, prices, URLs) must go in config/store.config.js

## Naming
- Components: PascalCase (ProductCard.js)
- Utils/pages: camelCase (priceFormatter.js)
- CSS classes: Tailwind only, no custom CSS except in output.css
